1 que. To view what's written in a file.
ans . - cat day-1
the first day project of 90 days of davops.


2 que. To change the access permissions of files.
ans. - command, (chmod 777 folder name ) to change the permission of the files,  chmod 777 day-1


3 que. - To check which commands you have run till nowe. 
ans.- history to cheak which commands tou have run till now.


4 que. - To remove a directory/ Folder
ans. - commands rm (file name) 


5 que. - To create a fruits.txt file and to view the content
  ans.- vim fruit.tx
        cat fruit.txt
        the file created for the task of 90 days of devops.


6 que. - Add content in devops.txt (One in each line) - Apple, Mango, Banana, Cherry, Kiwi, Orange, Guava.
  ans. - cat fruit.txt
