7 que. - To Show only top three fruits from the file.
  ans. -  head -n 3 fruit.txt
the file created for the task of 90 days of devops.
apple
mango


 8 que - To Show only bottom three fruits from the file.
ans -  tail -n 4 fruit.txt
kiwi
orange
guava


